<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed by Administrator</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        
        .password-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
            border: 2px solid #FF9933;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .password-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF9933, #138808);
        }
        
        .security-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #FF9933;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .password-title {
            color: #138808;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .password-message {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .new-password {
            background: #f0f8f0;
            border: 2px solid #138808;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #138808;
            word-break: break-all;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .new-password-label {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 153, 51, 0.3);
            margin: 10px;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 153, 51, 0.4);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .security-notice {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .security-notice h4 {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .security-notice p {
            color: #666;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .warning-info {
            background: #fff3e0;
            border: 1px solid #ff9800;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #e65100;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 20px 0;
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            .new-password {
                font-size: 16px;
                padding: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üîê Password Changed by Administrator</h1>
            <p>Your account password has been updated</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #333;">
                Hi {{firstName}},
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 25px; color: #666;">
                An administrator has changed the password for your Indians in Ghana membership account.
            </p>
            
            <div class="password-card">
                <div class="security-icon">üîë</div>
                <h2 class="password-title">New Password Assigned</h2>
                <p class="password-message">
                    Your new temporary password has been generated. Please use this password to log in and change it immediately for security reasons.
                </p>
                
                <div class="new-password-label">Your New Password:</div>
                <div class="new-password">{{tempPassword}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-notice">
                <h4>üõ°Ô∏è Important Security Information</h4>
                <p><strong>Account Details:</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Account: {{email}}</li>
                    <li>Full Name: {{fullName}}</li>
                    <li>Password changed by: Administrator</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning-info">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Steps:</strong>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Log in using the new password immediately</li>
                    <li>Change this temporary password to a strong, unique password</li>
                    <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
                    <li>If you didn't expect this change, contact support immediately</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #f0f8f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0;">
                <h4 style="color: #138808; margin-bottom: 15px;">üîí Next Steps:</h4>
                <ol style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Click the "Login Now" button</li>
                    <li>Enter your email and the new password provided</li>
                    <li>Go to your profile settings</li>
                    <li>Change your password to something secure and memorable</li>
                    <li>Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px;">
                <p style="color: #666; margin: 0;">
                    <strong>Need Help?</strong><br>
                    If you have any questions or concerns about this password change, please contact our support team at cards@indiansinghana.com.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>Email: cards@indiansinghana.com | Website: www.indiansinghana.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
